OverHistory.NewCommentry: Glenn Maxwell to Abhishek Sharma Wicket
OverHistory.Commentry: Glenn Maxwell bowling to Abhishek Sharma, good length ball, pitching outside off stump, Abhishek Sharma plays a defensive back foot push WICKET Kane Williamson run out Shahbaz Ahmed (Sunrisers Hyderabad 0 Runs for 1 wickets)towards Covers
OverHistory.UPDCommentry: Another first ball wicket in this match!  Glenn Maxwell bowling to Abhishek Sharma, good length ball, pitching outside off stump, Abhishek Sharma nudges this ball towards covers and the duo tries to steal a single. The fielder is quick enough to collect and throw the ball to the stumps directly! The bat is just on the line and Kane has depart without facing a single ball. WICKET!! Kane Williamson run out Shahbaz Ahmed (Sunrisers Hyderabad 0 Runs for 1 wicket)
